# Placeholder for the rendered example.pdf.
#
# The PDF gets generated on first scaffold-mode round-trip:
#   npm run render:pdf
#
# It is intentionally NOT committed to the plugin repo because:
# (a) PDF rendering depends on the user's local Pandoc + texlive + fonts
#     install — embedding a snapshot would be misleading about reproducibility.
# (b) The structural verification beat (checklist item 12) is the canonical
#     proof that the pipeline round-trips end-to-end.
# (c) Binary artifacts in plugin repos bloat clone times for marketplace users.
